## Schema reference

See `core/skills/billing/SKILL.md` for the schema that this file follows. The `billing` skill reads this file at every gate close (when PROJECT_TYPE: client) to compute invoices.

## Related files

- `foundation/CONTRACT.md` - has PROJECT_TYPE flag pointing here
- `foundation/INVOICES.md` - append-only ledger of invoices generated against this client
- `foundation/HANDOFF/` - created at v1.0.0 final gate

## Privacy

This file is committed to the project's git repo. If you don't want client info in the repo, add `foundation/CLIENTS.md` to `.gitignore` and keep client data outside source control. The `billing` skill will still read from disk; only the file's git-tracked status changes.
